<section id="panel-novios-section" class="hidden py-12 bg-stone-900 text-white px-4 md:px-6 border-t-4 border-wedding-gold">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
      <h3 class="font-title text-lg md:text-xl text-pirate-gold flex items-center space-x-2">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i>
        <span>Creador de Enlaces para Invitados</span>
      </h3>
      <button onclick="togglePanelNovios()" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-white transition text-xs uppercase font-bold">Cerrar</button>
    </div>

    <p class="text-xs text-stone-300">
      Escribe el nombre del invitado y su número de pases. Este panel generará un enlace único que prellenará la invitación y creará un mensaje de WhatsApp ideal para enviar de inmediato.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-stone-800 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-stone-700 space-y-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-stone-400 mb-2">Nombre del Invitado(s)</label>
          <input type="text" id="gen-name" placeholder="Ej: Tío Carlos y Tía Sofía" class="w-full bg-stone-700 border border-stone-600 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-sm outline-none focus:border-wedding-gold text-white" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-stone-400 mb-2">Número de Pases Reservados</label>
          <select id="gen-passes" class="w-full bg-stone-700 border border-stone-600 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-sm outline-none focus:border-wedding-gold text-white">
            <option value="1">1 Pase</option>
            <option value="2" selected>2 Pases</option>
            <option value="3">3 Pases</option>
            <option value="4">4 Pases</option>
            <option value="5">5 Pases</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="block text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-stone-400 mb-2">URL Base de tu Web de Boda (Opcional)</label>
        <input type="text" id="gen-base-url" placeholder="Dejar vacío para usar la dirección actual" class="w-full bg-stone-700 border border-stone-600 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-sm outline-none focus:border-wedding-gold text-white" />
      </div>

      <div class="pt-2">
        <button onclick="generarInvitacionLink()" class="w-full bg-wedding-gold hover:bg-amber-600 text-stone-950 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs py-3 rounded-full transition flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i>
          <span>Generar Link e Invitación</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="gen-result-container" class="hidden bg-stone-800 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-stone-700 space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-stone-400 mb-1">Enlace Personalizado Único:</label>
        <div class="flex space-x-2">
          <input type="text" id="gen-result-url" readonly class="w-full bg-stone-900 border border-stone-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-2 text-xs text-amber-400 outline-none" />
          <button onclick="copiarAlPortapapelesId('gen-result-url')" class="bg-stone-700 hover:bg-stone-600 px-4 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold transition">Copiar</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="block text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-stone-400 mb-1">Mensaje de WhatsApp Sugerido:</label>
        <textarea id="gen-result-msg" rows="4" readonly class="w-full bg-stone-900 border border-stone-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-2 text-xs text-stone-200 outline-none font-sans"></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2">
        <button onclick="copiarAlPortapapelesId('gen-result-msg')" class="flex-1 bg-stone-700 hover:bg-stone-600 text-white font-bold uppercase text-xxs py-2.5 rounded-full transition">
          Copiar Mensaje
        </button>
        <button onclick="compartirWhatsAppDirecto()" class="flex-1 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold uppercase text-xxs py-2.5 rounded-full transition flex items-center justify-center space-x-1">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-lg"></i>
          <span>Enviar por WhatsApp</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="bg-stone-950 text-white py-12 md:py-16 px-4 md:px-6 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6 relative z-10">
    <h2 class="anim-fade-in-up font-title text-2xl md:text-3xl text-pirate-gold">¡Nos vemos en la Gran Ruta de la Vida!</h2>
    <p class="anim-fade-in-up text-stone-300 font-serif-elegant italic max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm md:text-lg">
      "Un pirata no olvida a sus nakamas, y un shinobi nunca rompe una promesa. ¡Gracias por acompañarnos en este gran paso!"
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6 py-4 md:py-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-pirate-gold">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-anchor float-animation"></i>
      <i class="fa-solid fa-heart animate-pulse"></i>
      <i class="fa-solid fa-leaf float-animation" style="animation-delay: 2s"></i>
    </div>

    <p class="text-[10px] md:text-stone-400 font-mono tracking-widest uppercase block">
      Débora Colón & Pablo Díaz — Bodas 2027
    </p>

    <button onclick="togglePanelNovios()" class="mt-4 text-[10px] text-stone-500 hover:text-wedding-gold font-bold uppercase tracking-widest transition">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-lock mr-1"></i>Panel de Novios
    </button>
  </div>
</footer>
